title: #92Noon! Vox in the Box! Evason/Hersch/Russo/Birk/Walz
description: --Vox in the Box is back for the playoffs! Dean Evason joins right away to give his thoughts heading into game 3, Jaime Hersch talks being a Wild Fan at NHL Network, Russo talks his Wild insight, Birk Bit, and Wes Walz previews game 3.
